arts.ttl: Marseille looks to follow up Ligue 1 win against PSG with victory at Strasbourg
arts.sum: After scoring twice last weekend in a 5-2 win against Metz, Fati could start on Saturday away to struggling Lorient — whose defense has leaked 13 goals in five games. Marseille’s victory was its first home win in Ligue 1 against PSG for 14 years.

arts.ttl: Geoffrey Kondogbia and Junior Hamad Traoré ruled out of Marseille trip to Strasbourg
arts.sum: During his pre-match press conference attended by Get French Football News, Marseille manager Roberto De Zerbi has ruled out Geoffrey Kondogbia and Junior Hamad Traoré out of his side’s trip…
